snippet.title: Dark Rage - Platformer Trailer
snippet.description:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.coldteam.darkrage.ultimate
Platformer that combines adventure, RPG and exciting action.
In Dark Rage - you play as a resurrected knight.
Even death will not stop the brave hero, only bloodthirsty zombies, revived skeletons and other monsters stand in your way. With Fire and sword, destroy enemies, absorbing their souls. Explore sinister dungeon with dangerous traps and treasures.
Equip armor and weapons, improve skills and fight in fierce battles.
